{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_StaffAttack}}
'''A_StaffAttack''' (int ''damage'', string ''puff'')<br>

Performs a melee attack for ''damage'' point and using ''puff'' as the puff type. If the given puff type is invalid, {{Class|BulletPuff}} is used as a fall-back. The player using the calling weapon also turns to face the target, if any.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Staff}} and derived classes.

